<D>__{yeah. it's on tv...}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{in southeast asia? it there, too?}
<P>__{(beat)}
<D>__{that's a joke, man...!}
<A>__{ali hangs up. the phone rings again.}
<C>__{ali }
<P>__{(frustrated)}
<D>__{what do i think about who? vietcong?}
<A>__{next is something ali has not deduced. ali perceives it intuitively and reflexively. as with other of his decisions, once made, he doesn't hesitate to speak them. and he won't waver. he says...}
<C>__{ali }
<D>__{man, i ain't got no quarrel with them vietcong.}
